<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">上述列表中的基金可参与费率优惠活动，<span style="COLOR: black; mso-themecolor: text1">具体优惠规则以汇成基金的安排为准。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>
